data.description: .5 Miles within Tipton county so all the benefits of low taxes and awesome schools, but still close to Shelby county for work if needed. featuring a 20' great-room, 4br down plus bonus up, new stain-master carpet, luxury vinyl plank in all living areas, new roof spring of 23, 15x25 wired workshop, 1 acre lot, 10' walk in pantry, Large shade trees backyard(recently pruned), city water and septic system (pumped Oct 2020), Nice size main bedroom with walk-in closet. This just might be the one!!
